==Demographics==
As of 2010, only one person lived in Monowi: a white female named Elsie Eiler, born 1933, living alone in one of the town's three housing units, the others unoccupied.<ref name="wwwcensusgov">{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov|title=2010 Demographic Profile Data – Monowi village, Nebraska|publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]|access-date=October 8, 2018}}</ref>

